title: Ultimate GameDev Tutorials by Eteeski Tutorials
description:
DESCRIPTION:

Eteeski Tutorials (now known as "Master Indie") created a kickstarter for a Unity 4 Game Developing tutorial: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/eteeski/ultimate-gamedev-tutorials-make-your-first-video-g 
The Kickstarter was successful and Eteeskie created the first season on his youtube channel.
However, Eteeski left his company and ended the production of the tutorials. He wanted to distance himself from the company,so he removed the tutorials from his youtube channel, and renamed the youtube channel.
Link to the channel:

Since the tutorials are no longer available, I am going to upload this torrent, and keep it until the tutorials are available again.

CONTENTS (In a .rar file):

GameDev Tutorials 1
Readme
Shmup Tutorial (for people who want to use Javascript instead of C#)
Video Descriptions (not for shmup)
Info about Eteeski


NOTE: These tutorials work with unity 5, but some code will need to be changed (e.g. GetComponent will need to be used)
